### Criar notícia (autenticado)
POST http://localhost:3000/news
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer replace-with-token

{
  "title": "Nova descoberta científica",
  "summary": "Cientistas fazem descoberta revolucionária",
  "content": "Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Sed do eiusmod tempor incididunt ut labore et dolore magna aliqua. Ut enim ad minim veniam, quis nostrud exercitation ullamco laboris nisi ut aliquip ex ea commodo consequat.",
  "coverImageUrl": "https://example.com/image.jpg",
  "category": "ciencia",
  "tags": ["ciencia", "descoberta"],
  "featured": true,
  "status": "published"
}

### Buscar notícia por ID
GET http://localhost:3000/news/replace-with-uuid

### Atualizar notícia (autenticado)
PUT http://localhost:3000/news/replace-with-uuid
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer replace-with-token

{
  "title": "Título atualizado",
  "featured": false
}

### Deletar notícia (autenticado)
DELETE http://localhost:3000/news/replace-with-uuid
Authorization: Bearer replace-with-token

### Listar últimas notícias
GET http://localhost:3000/news/latest?page=1&perPage=10

### Listar últimas notícias por categoria
GET http://localhost:3000/news/latest/ciencia?page=1&perPage=10
